data.description: Welcome to your spacious oasis, right here New Bern, NC! This immaculately maintained home boasts an impressive five bedrooms and three baths, providing ample space for family and guests alike.Step inside to discover a seamless blend of comfort and style, with luxury vinyl plank (LVP) and plush carpet flooring (both installed in 2024) throughout, ensuring both durability and coziness. The bathrooms feature easy-to-maintain vinyl flooring for added convenience.The kitchen boasts an almost new Frigidaire refrigerator and dishwasher, a GE glass top stove and built-in microwave; the new glass and grout backsplash adds the perfect touch of detail.Entertain with ease in the elegant dining room, which opens out into a screened porch, offering the perfect spot for enjoying meals or simply unwinding with a book while taking in the serene views of the surrounding greenery. Step out onto the adjacent patio, ideal for hosting summer barbecues or sipping your morning coffee in the crisp air.Your outdoor retreat awaits in the fenced backyard, complete with a wood privacy fence, providing a sense of seclusion and security. Whether you're letting your pets roam freely or hosting gatherings with loved ones, this private sanctuary is sure to become your favorite spot to relax and recharge.Conveniently located in the sought-after Croatan Woods neighborhood, this home offers easy access to nearby amenities, including shopping, dining, parks, and more. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional property your own - schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of Southern charm and comfort!
